# Newsboat colour scheme

color background          color0    default
color listnormal          white     default
color listnormal_unread   color2    default
color listfocus           white     color237
color listfocus_unread    color2    color237
color info                color3    color234
color article             white     default

# highlights
highlight article  "^(Feed|Link):.*$"         color2    default bold
highlight article  "^(Title):.*$"             color5    default bold
highlight article  "^(Date|Author):.*$"       color166  default
highlight article  "https?://[^ ]+"           color4    default underline
highlight article  "\\[[0-9]+\\]"             color10   default bold
highlight article  "\\[image\\ [0-9]+\\]"     color3    default bold
highlight article  "c[0-9]+( part[0-9])?"     color2    default bold
highlight article  "v[0-9]+"                  color2    default
highlight feedlist "^â”€.*$"                    color6    default bold
